**Company:** {{ ticker }} ({{ company_name }})
**Sector:** {{ sector }}

### FILTER AGENT — Hard Metrics Gates

**Metrics Provided:**
- Gross Margin: {{ gross_margin | format('%.1%') or 'N/A' }}
- ROIC: {{ roic | format('%.1%') or 'N/A' }}
- 3Y Revenue Growth: {{ revenue_growth_3yr | format('%.1%') or 'N/A' }}
- Net Debt / EBITDA: {{ net_debt_ebitda | format('%.1f') or 'N/A' }}x

**Thresholds:**
- Min Gross Margin: {{ min_gross_margin | format('%.0%') }}
- Min ROIC: {{ min_roic | format('%.0%') }}
- Min 3Y Growth: {{ min_growth | format('%.0%') }}
- Max Leverage: {{ max_leverage | format('.1f') }}x

**Assessment:** Evaluate each metric against threshold. FAIL if ANY falls below floor.

