### BUSINESS MODEL AGENT — Clarity Check

**Company Description:**
> {{ description }}

**Business Segments:**
{% if segments %}
{% for seg in segments %}
- {{ seg.name }}: {{ seg.revenue_pct | format('%.0%') }} of revenue
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
(No segment data available)
{% endif %}

**Assessment:** Can you explain this business in one sentence? If not, or if it's a conglomerate, FAIL.

