### RED FLAG AGENT — Red Flag Detection

**Capital Allocation Concerns:**
- Buyback to FCF Ratio: {{ buyback_fcf_ratio | format('x') or 'N/A' }}
- Stock-Based Compensation: {{ sbc | format('$M') or 'N/A' }} ({{ sbc_to_revenue | format('%.1%') or 'N/A' }} of revenue)
- Stock Dilution Rate: {{ dilution_rate | format('%.1%') or 'N/A' }}
- APIC Growth vs RE Growth: {{ apic_vs_re | format('x') or 'N/A' }}

**Cash Flow Concerns:**
- FCF to CapEx: {{ fcf_to_capex | format('%.1%') or 'N/A' }}
- Leverage: {{ leverage | format('.1f') or 'N/A' }}x ND/EBITDA

**Learned Patterns (Recent Analyst Feedback):**
{% if learned_patterns %}
{% for pattern in learned_patterns %}
- {{ pattern.issue }} (confidence: {{ pattern.confidence | format('%.0%') }})
  Current: {{ pattern.current_value | format('x') }}, Suggested Threshold: {{ pattern.suggested_threshold | format('x') }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
(No learned patterns yet — first run with this company)
{% endif %}

**Assessment:** Flag if:
- Buyback > 1.0x FCF
- Stock dilution > 2%
- APIC growing faster than RE
- FCF/CapEx < 50%
- Leverage > 5.0x
- OR learned pattern matches with high confidence

